                                                           -*- rst -*-
                            ====================
                             BRAID INSTALLATION
                            ====================


CONTENTS
========

  Requirements
  Process


REQUIREMENTS
============

  Braid is dependent on the installation of following software packages:

  *  Languages
  *  Make


PROCESS
=======

  Assuming you are currently at the root of the package
directory and you have the necessary software and environment, 
simply type the following::

   $ mkdir build && cd build && ../configure --prefix=<INSTALL_DIR> && make install


